# Ignored modernization suggestions
# Format: <date> <category> <description>
2026-06-15 newexpr new(expr) (Go 1.26) is cryptic for pointer-to-literal in tests (new(0.25) reads as an allocation, not a *float64 = 0.25) and editor gopls on go<1.26 flags it as NotAType; use the generic ptr[T] helper in mcpserver/rerank_internal_test.go instead
